    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly in showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it looks absolutely pristine! It drives like a total dream and still has that 'new car' feel that's so hard to find. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in top-notch shape, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
